The key to controlling the external=
 world is in controlling the internal world. The key to controlling the int=
ernal world is in recognizing the paramount role of one's own conditioning =
in *moulding* the internal world. In the end, it all boils down to self-con=
trol and overcoming one's conditioning.
=C2=A0
