dating. Why is she so mean to me". If one suppresses that feeling and force=
s nice behavior, that is good only temporarily. The character of wife in on=
e's inner world is still a negative one. One's thoughts about that characte=
r are still "I am being so nice and accommodating. Why is she so mean to me=
". The suppressed resentment will blow off oneday and result in a bigger fi=
ght/argument.
=C2=A0
